## ğŸª Retailer Logos

### Active Retailers
- **GroceryCo**: Main supermarket chain
- **FreshMart**: Fresh produce and specialty items
- **MeatMarket**: Meat specialist
- **DeliCorner**: Deli meats and specialty items
- **BakeryPlus**: Bakery items
- **DairyDirect**: Dairy products specialist
- **SuperSave**: Discount retailer (referenced in cart system)

